---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Waluigi | Christopher Audretsch">
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 py-8 md:py-16">
    <h1 class="font-serif text-3xl md:text-4xl font-semibold text-text mb-8 md:mb-10">Waluigi</h1>

    <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
      <p>
        Sam's practice of lending customer deposits meant humanity's pandemic-prevention research
        depended on Sam's fortune and the gambles he was willing to take to increase it.
      </p>

      <p>
        Bankman-Fried's bankman's creed banked man's "man: disease-freed" leads on Bankman's greed.
      </p>

      <img src="/waluigisbf.png" class="rounded-lg" />

      <p>
        Investments from financial institutions and customers' need for a better exchange led him
        to do the things he did, Sam argues.
      </p>

      <p>
        Bank's seeds, man's needs feed bankman-Fried's deeds, bankman-fried pleads.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
